      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA WHISKEY (1) is a progressive dog who scored his 2nd career win last time at Geelong, scoring by half a length (26.19). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Expected to be right there at the finish again. PERFECT SYMPHONY (2) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when second (29.77) over 515m at this track. Well placed and gets her chance. BRAVE ISLAND (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.69) in a Mix 6/7 at this track. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. JILLIBY PIXIE (3) put a gap on her rivals last start. Big chance on that form.",
